Package: hetid
Title: Identification Through Heteroskedasticity a La Lewbel (2012)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Fernando", "Duarte", , "fernando_duarte@brown.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8495-6936"))
Author: Fernando Duarte [aut, cre]
    (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-8495-6936>)
Maintainer: Fernando Duarte <fernando_duarte@brown.edu>
Description: Implements identification through heteroskedasticity methods
    including Klein and Vella (2010), Lewbel (2012), Rigobon (2003), and
    Prono (2014) for models with endogenous regressors. Provides tools for
    estimation and inference when traditional instruments are not
    available.
